%ACnh-L%E1%BB%A5c-t%E1%BB%83/poem-ItCtAZWsVjvFWSP4GmlZOg">Đề Hành Sơn huyện Văn Tuyên Vương miếu tân học đường, trình Lục tể - 題衡山縣文宣王廟新學堂呈陸宰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Mi%E1%BB%87n/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-ho%E1%BA%A1-mai/poem-xOogqNjbaXknquxnAP16aQ">Đề hoạ mai - 題畫梅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Mi%E1%BB%87n/author-fEGcjpEMDS77hLL_7VN-Wg">Vương Miện</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/H%E1%BA%A1-Gi%E1%BB%9Bi-Hi%C3%AAn-c%C3%B4ng-tr%E1%BB%AB-nhi%E1%BA%BFp-h%E1%BB%AFu-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1/poem-NlW0prdbtNIR_yAo48UQ-w">Hạ Giới Hiên công trừ nhiếp hữu bộc xạ - 賀介軒公除攝右僕射</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/H%C3%A0nh-l%E1%BB%99-nan-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-cEtFYbkmI1o3u3iBnSrHGQ">Hành lộ nan kỳ 2 - 行路難其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Sa-Gi%E1%BA%A3-th%C3%A1i-ph%C3%B3/poem-xEsRxN5L9eDUR5ntEPNuXA">Trường Sa Giả thái phó - 長沙賈太傅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%C3%BD-ca-h%C3%A0nh-Bi%E1%BB%87t-t%C3%B2ng-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87t-C%E1%BA%A7n-l%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-quy-c%E1%BA%A7n-nh%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1c-khuy%E1%BA%BFn/poem-4WfIEG4ivnwdSAmKNxd6BA">Tuý ca hành - Biệt tòng điệt Cần lạc đệ quy, cần nhất tác khuyến - 醉歌行－別從侄勤落第歸，勤一作勸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
